{"id":9966,"date":"2020-12-11T04:25:45","date_gmt":"2020-12-11T04:25:45","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/?p=9966"},"modified":"2021-07-06T01:40:41","modified_gmt":"2021-07-06T01:40:41","slug":"mau-sac-cua-nam-2021","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/mau-sac-cua-nam-2021\/","title":{"rendered":"X\u00c1M TRUNG T\u00cdNH L\u00c0 1 TRONG 2 M\u00c0U S\u1eaeC C\u1ee6A N\u0102M 2021"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Kh\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi danh hi\u1ec7u \u201cm\u00e0u s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a n\u0103m 2021\u201d \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ec7n Pantone g\u1ecdi t\u00ean l\u00e0 2 m\u00e0u Illuminating (v\u00e0ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1) v\u00e0 Ultimate Gray (x\u00e1m t\u1ed1i th\u01b0\u1ee3ng). C\u00f3 l\u1ebd qua hai m\u00e0u s\u1eafc n\u00e0y, Pantone mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi g\u1eafm hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2021 t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng h\u01a1n, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u01a1n sau m\u1ed9t n\u0103m 2020 \u0111\u1ea7y bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9ng.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/mau-sac-cua-nam-2021-2.jpg\" alt=\"mau-sac-cua-nam-2021\" class=\"wp-image-9967\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/mau-sac-cua-nam-2021-2.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/mau-sac-cua-nam-2021-2-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/mau-sac-cua-nam-2021-2-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Sau nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e1ng c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia c\u1ee7a c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7n Pantone l\u00f9ng s\u1ee5c kh\u1eafp th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 ghi nh\u1eadn l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a th\u1eddi trang, xe h\u01a1i, n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t,&#8230; nh\u1eefng th\u1ee9 xung quanh cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng con ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0 t\u00ecm ra m\u00e0u s\u1eafc ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a n\u0103m 2021. Hai m\u00e0u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ec7n m\u00e0u s\u1eafc l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t:&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>Illuminating l\u00e0 m\u00e0u v\u00e0ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1, t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 vui v\u1ebb. L\u1ea5y c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi, truy\u1ec1n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng v\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng.<\/li><li>Ultimate Gray, m\u1ed9t m\u00e0u x\u00e1m trung t\u00ednh, l\u00e0 bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a tr\u00ed tu\u1ec7, c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc, \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u00e2y, t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i v\u0129nh c\u1eedu v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc. M\u00e0u s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng vi\u00ean s\u1ecfi tr\u00ean b\u00e3i bi\u1ec3n v\u00e0 c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng ch\u1ecdi v\u1edbi th\u1eddi gian, Ultimate Gray mang l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u0129nh, \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i.&nbsp;<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/mau-sac-cua-nam-2021-1-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9968\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/mau-sac-cua-nam-2021-1-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/mau-sac-cua-nam-2021-1-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/mau-sac-cua-nam-2021-1-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/mau-sac-cua-nam-2021-1-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/mau-sac-cua-nam-2021-1.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2, Pantone ch\u1ecdn hai m\u00e0u l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n thay v\u00ec ch\u1ecdn m\u1ed9t. L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2016 v\u1edbi hai m\u00e0u h\u1ed3ng th\u1ea1ch anh v\u00e0 xanh thanh b\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p ph\u1ea3n \u00e1nh t\u00ednh c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 linh ho\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a gi\u1edbi t\u00ednh v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u0103m 2021, hai t\u00f4ng m\u00e0u x\u00e1m &#8211; v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed9c l\u1eadp v\u00e0 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea3n nhau, nh\u01b0ng khi k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhau s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t c\u1eb7p m\u00e0u \u0111\u1ea7y kh\u00e1t v\u1ecdng, k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i nh\u1eefng c\u1ea3m x\u00fac s\u00e2u s\u1eafc h\u01a1n v\u1edbi mong mu\u1ed1n v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y tr\u00e0n ng\u1eadp \u00e1nh n\u1eafng. D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0u s\u1eafc ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1o trong nhi\u1ec1u thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a n\u0103m 2021.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Trong thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, m\u00e0u x\u00e1m ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft hot, b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u00e0u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ed3n m\u00e3i v\u1edbi th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0 mang s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a uy quy\u1ec1n. V\u1edbi m\u00e0u x\u00e1m ch\u00fang ta d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng nhi\u1ec1u t\u00f4ng m\u00e0u kh\u00e1c nhau \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1 t\u00ednh, gu th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>S\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a m\u00e0u v\u00e0ng g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o v\u00e0 cho ta c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng tr\u00e0n ng\u1eadp n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft c\u1ee7a tu\u1ed5i tr\u1ebb.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/mau-sac-cua-nam-2021-5-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"mau-sac-cua-nam-2021\" class=\"wp-image-9970\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/mau-sac-cua-nam-2021-5-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/mau-sac-cua-nam-2021-5-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/mau-sac-cua-nam-2021-5-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/mau-sac-cua-nam-2021-5-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/mau-sac-cua-nam-2021-5-2048x1366.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/mau-sac-cua-nam-2021-5-scaled.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Ng\u00e0y nay, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc d\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c giao ti\u1ebfp th\u00ec trong ng\u00e0nh n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e3, \u0111ang v\u00e0 v\u1eabn ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef c\u1ee7a m\u00e0u s\u1eafc nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ea1t suy ngh\u0129, \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c, k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nhau. H\u00e3y \u0111\u00f3n ch\u1edd nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o, \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1eeb hai m\u00e0u s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a n\u0103m 2021 nh\u00e9.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>&gt;&gt; Xem th\u00eam:  <a href=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/noi-that-chung-cu-goldmark-city\/\">Thi\u1ebft K\u1ebf N\u1ed9i Th\u1ea5t Chung C\u01b0 Goldmark City<\/a> <\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>&gt;&gt; Xem th\u00eam:  <a href=\"https:\/\/byzan.v